name: Star girl #2
description: Collection of 3D art "STAR GIRL". The art is stylized for 90s computer graphics and revolves around the girls in whose lives a key moment occurred, the moment when the main need is to be alone with oneself. Heroines have different social status, different professions and different views on life, but now they are closer than ever: next to only a favorite car, cigarette smoke and a look at the sky.
